OL,3,CCountry isn't crying out for Polanski
OL,4,Cor Farage, Labour minister claims
OL,6,FThe Labour MP was speaking on ITV
OL,7,FMeridian's political programme, The
OL,8,FLast Word, ahead of local elections in
OL,9,Fparts of the South on 7 May.
OL,11,FMr Ward ` who was a speechwriter for
OL,12,FSir Keir Starmer in opposition ` added
OL,13,Fthat the local elections were coming
OL,14,Fat a "difficult time in the electoral
OL,15,Fcycle" for Labour and follow the
OL,16,F"disappointing" by-election defeat in
OL,17,FGorton and Denton.
OL,26,@vD@FOUwD@FO]xD@AOUxD@OO]
