OL,3,CCountry isn't crying out for Polanski
OL,4,Cor Farage, Labour minister claims
OL,6,FResponding to the minister's comment
OL,7,Fabout Nigel Farage, a Reform UK
OL,8,Fspokesman said: "The only change
OL,9,FLabour are delivering is higher taxes,
OL,10,Fhigher prices, and record illegal
OL,11,Fimmigration."
OL,13,FPolling day will include elections all
OL,14,Fcounty council seats in Essex, East
OL,15,FSussex, West Sussex and Hampshire.
OL,16,FUnitary councils with all seats to
OL,17,Fplay for include the new authorities
OL,18,Fof East and West Surrey, as well as
OL,19,Fthe Isle of Wight, Thurrock and
OL,20,FSwindon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
