OL,3,CCountry isn't crying out for Polanski
OL,4,Cor Farage, Labour minister claims
OL,6,FThe Green peer, Baroness Jones of
OL,7,FMoulsecombe, said her party leader had
OL,8,Fbeen "extremely clever" in "taking the
OL,9,Ffight" to Nigel Farage.
OL,11,FJenny Jones told The Last Word that
OL,12,FZach Polanski was offering the
OL,13,Felectorate "completely the opposite"
OL,14,Fto Reform UK and predicted the Greens
OL,15,Fwould "win big" at the local elections.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@WO]pD@\OUqD@FO]uD@LOUuD@dO]wD@
OL,26,AGOUwD@OO]
