OL,3,CCountry isn't crying out for Polanski
OL,4,Cor Farage, Labour minister claims
OL,6,FThe Conservatives' Donna Jones, who is
OL,7,FHampshire and the Isle of Wight's
OL,8,Fpolice and crime commissioners, said:
OL,9,F"People are voting either Green, or
OL,10,Ffor the Conservative Party, or for
OL,11,Fother parties to try and stop Reform
OL,12,Ffrom winning here in the South Coast.
OL,14,F"I think that's what we're going to
OL,15,Fsee in Hampshire and the Isle of
OL,16,FWight."
OL,18,FReform UK's leader has been touring
OL,19,Fthe South of England this week, with
OL,20,Frallies in Newport on the Isle of
OL,21,FWight and Basingstoke in Hampshire.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOUxD@GO]
