OL,3,CCountry isn't crying out for Polanski
OL,4,Cor Farage, Labour minister claims
OL,6,FSpeaking on the Isle of Wight, Nigel
OL,7,FFarage said: "The whole council is up
OL,8,Ffor election and we're here to say:
OL,9,Fwe're the new kids on the block, give
OL,10,Fus a chance."
OL,12,FThe Liberal Democrats' Calum Miller
OL,13,Fsaid his party were "hoping to win a
OL,14,Ffew more seats from the Conservatives
OL,15,Fand to hold onto the ones we have."
OL,17,FThe Bicester and Woodstock MP added:
OL,18,F"People recognise that they already
OL,19,Fhave wardworking Lib Dem councillors
OL,20,Fand they're looking to elect some
OL,21,Fmore."
OL,26,@oD@NOUrD@MO]uD@UOUwD@cO]zD@AOU}D@FO]
